# Google OAuth Client ID
# 1. Go to https://console.cloud.google.com
# 2. Create a project (or select existing)
# 3. APIs & Services → Credentials → Create → OAuth 2.0 Client ID → Web application
# 4. Add Authorized JavaScript origins:
#      http://localhost:3000
#      https://your-ngrok-url.ngrok-free.app  (replace with your ngrok URL)
# 5. Paste your Client ID below, then copy this file to .env and restart the dev server

VITE_GOOGLE_CLIENT_ID=your_google_client_id_here.apps.googleusercontent.com
